<p class="terms-text"><span class="s1">EXAMPLES OF TYPES OF PRAISE AND CRITICISM</span></p>
<p class="terms-text"><span class="s1">“Praise” can be defined as a ‘ Positive expression of approval’ -‐ e.g.:</span></p>
<ul class="ul1">
